bade time baad Gurdas Maan di koi film aai hai te mainu dekhan da mauka lag gia jaldi hi. so review likha rihan.
samjh nahi a rahi film dian changian gallan ton shuru kita jave ja khaamian ton. khair changian ton e shuru karna chahida hai. Rimpy Prince di eh pehli movie hai te uhna ne wadia kam kita hai so es karke oh wadhai de patar ne. Gurdas Maan, Vivek Shauq te Manav Vij di acting sarahun yog hai.
hun gal karde an kamian di. 2 cheezan sab ton waddian ne. Gurdas Maan ne enne wadde wadde role play kite ne k aam role uhde kadd unsar bahut chota lagda te hamesha eh feeling aaundi k insaaf nahi ho riha Gurdas Maan naal. because he is capable of doing a loadz more. dooji kami sare actors di. Gurdas Maan, Vivek Shauq te Manav Vij nu shad ke almost sare e actor Punjabi bolan lai sangarsh kar rahe c. lagda uhna da sara dhiyan Punjabi dialoge bolan ch lag riha c rather than acting. te sab kuch kinna nakli nakli ja lagda c. music b film da ok ok hi c. kuch gaane theek c te baki sara kam jaldi jaldi ch hoya lagda c. poore mahol ch koi jaan e nahi c. gurdas maan te vivek shauq e rule kar rahe c jado hor koi character screen te aaunda c tan gal nahi ban rahi c.
film de end te dharaman wala message bahut wadia tareeke naal ditta hai&hellip;really appreciable&hellip;
khair meri soch unusaar film te sari galbaat gurdas maan di kadd di nahi c&hellip;
